<L>__{int ext il passetto night}
<A>__{vittoria and langdon race up a flight of stairs, and the passetto comes out into the open for a hundred yards or so as it leaves the castel sant'angelo. ahead, they see a rope ladder over the side. they look down. directly below them, mr. gray is getting into an alfa romeo parked discretely at the end of a dead end street, making his escape. down on the street, the car door slams. in the car, mr. gray turns the key. up on the passetto, langdon and vittoria are running toward the vatican again when the explosion rips through the still night. they stagger and turn back, in time to see mr. gray's car go up in an enormous fireball.}
